<p>The B/W generation began in 2010 following the Japanese release of Pok&eacute;mon Black and White. It introduced 156 new Pok&eacute;mon, triple and rotation battles, and the Pok&eacute;mon Dream World. B/W is played online on the simulator <a href="http://pokemonshowdown.com">Pok√©mon Showdown</a>!</p>


